{"word":"τειχέω","slug":"τειχέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>τειχέω</b></el> <el>(τειχέω,) ( φυτ. <el>-ήσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <a href='S:τειχίζω'><el>τειχίζω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to build walls</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <el>τεῖχος τ.</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:transitive'>trans.</a> <i>to fortify</i>, <el>τὸν Ἰσθμόν</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}